00:01:37,981 --> 00:01:39,718
maybe the sun's here,
and it's shining out,

43
00:01:39,718 --> 00:01:41,603
and it's a beautiful day.

44
00:01:42,052 --> 00:01:44,704
We'll do this painting
mostly in brown tones.

45
00:01:44,756 --> 00:01:49,109
Sometimes it's gorgeous to do
paintings in just one tone.

46
00:01:50,094 --> 00:01:51,379
There we are.

47
00:01:53,563 --> 00:01:55,633
Mmm, all right.

48
00:01:55,634 --> 00:01:57,402
Now, then, I want to mix up a color.

49
00:01:57,402 --> 00:01:59,637
I like brown made from

