00:02:06,243 --> 00:02:08,195
a little bit to the reddish side.

54
00:02:08,447 --> 00:02:09,764
Just a small amount.

55
00:02:10,282 --> 00:02:12,933
Normally we don't worry
about mixing color too well.

56
00:02:12,984 --> 00:02:14,319
Today, I want to mix this pretty good,

57
00:02:14,318 --> 00:02:16,655
because I don't want any
green streaks up in the sky.

58
00:02:18,085 --> 00:02:19,000
Okay.

59
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,875
That ought to do it.

60
00:02:21,725 --> 00:02:22,978
Wipe the old knife,

