105
00:04:21,074 --> 00:04:23,014
to achieve a desire lightness.

106
00:04:23,014 --> 00:04:25,281
You can make it as light
or as bright as you want,

107
00:04:25,281 --> 00:04:27,084
but once you get our here
in these dark colors,

108
00:04:27,084 --> 00:04:29,553
I suggest that you clean the brush

109
00:04:29,553 --> 00:04:31,772
before you bring it back into the center.

110
00:04:32,958 --> 00:04:34,576
There we go.

111
00:04:35,660 --> 00:04:37,645
Something about like so.

112
00:04:38,295 --> 00:04:39,898
Once again, you can make it

113
00:04:39,898 --> 00:04:42,981
as light as you want it
when you do your painting.

114
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:46,021
Or leave it as dark as you want.

115
00:04:46,904 --> 00:04:48,883
It's really an individual thing.

116
00:04:48,884 --> 00:04:50,507
Now, very lightly.

