00:05:14,766 --> 00:05:17,085
and you beat it against
the easel the same way.

128
00:05:17,769 --> 00:05:19,086
All right.

129
00:05:20,437 --> 00:05:22,540
And just barely caress it,

130
00:05:22,540 --> 00:05:24,709
and the indication of a little sun

