00:05:24,709 --> 00:05:27,528
will remain right there
in your sky, that easy.

132
00:05:28,045 --> 00:05:28,932
See there?

133
00:05:28,932 --> 00:05:30,063
It's all you need.

134
00:05:30,382 --> 00:05:32,312
Okay, let's have some fun.

135
00:05:32,312 --> 00:05:33,717
We're still using the same old brush,

136
00:05:33,718 --> 00:05:35,887
a little white, a little
bit of that brown color

